1983 babies, we are turning 40 this year!! Can you believe it? We are full fledged adults! Who allowed this? @kevonstage & I  have decided to get into the best shape of our life in every aspect of our life:relationship, mental and physical health, and spiritually.  We started by looking for a way to spice up our date nights, so we’re taking a 6-week Improv class that ends in a live show. We are having an absolute blast!  It’s so much fun! But, the classes are 3 hours long, and we live extremely busy lives, so trying to ensure we have the energy to add another thing to our schedule is a challenge.  So we’ve partnered with @drinkorgain to help us reach our 2023 goals by helping us keep up our energy and motivation on our extremely busy days. Stay tuned for the journey. 

 #orgainpartner #thatorgainfeeling #keepitgoing2023
